Docs.summary: TermTransform builds up term vocabularies (dictionaries). Notes: * Each column builds/uses exactly one "vocabulary" (dictionary). * Output columns are KeyType-valued. * The Key value is the one-based index of the item in the dictionary. * Not found is assigned the value zero.
